snippet.description:
Valuetainment is a leading source of information for all.

Our Mission

TO ENLIGHTEN, ENTERTAIN AND EMPOWER CURRENT AND FUTURE LEADERS AROUND THE WORLD.

WHO WE ARE:

Valuetainment is the leading source for information, education and entertainment centered on the fundamentals of entrepreneurship and capitalism. •

WHY WE EXIST:

There is a need for a voice that carries the torch for entrepreneurship and capitalism, projecting a compelling, positive message. We are that voice. •

WHO WE SERVE:

Established and aspirational entrepreneurs, startup founders, students, intrapreneurs, and leaders within all types of organizations (public/private/non-profit). •

WHAT WE PROVIDE:

A slate of live and online events and a growing content library that includes: video series, digital courses, podcasts and scripted programming. This vast content offering is delivered through our website, distribution partners including YouTube and Spotify and our own OTT channel.

snippet.title: Behind the News
snippet.description:
For the past 50 years, BTN has been a world leader in children's news & kids news. As part of the Australian Broadcasting Corporation, BTN has introduced the news & current events to upper-primary students in Australia and around the world - but it isn't just for kids. BTN assists people of all ages by breaking down current issues and events in a high-energy, fun way - all while providing background information that isn’t usually given by other news bulletins.
 
We have 1000s of stories on all sorts of topics - if you're looking for help to understand something, you'll probably find it on BTN. http://www.abc.net.au/btn/ 

Follow us on Social Media:

snippet.title: NOS
snippet.description:
De NOS is de grootste nieuwsorganisatie van Nederland. Grote nieuwsgebeurtenissen kan je hier LIVE volgen. En elke vrijdagmiddag een nieuw RONDJE BINNENHOF, onze politieke YouTube-serie rondom de formatie. Mis niets en abonneer je op ons YouTube-kanaal.

Reageer ook vooral onder onze video's, we zijn benieuwd naar jouw mening. Dit YouTube-kanaal is een plek waar iedereen zich kan uitspreken, met respect voor elkaar. We willen geen scheldwoorden, beledigingen, bedreigingen, discriminatie, off-topic-berichten, spam en reclame-uitingen. We laten liefst alle reacties staan maar grijpen in als dat nodig en mogelijk is. Zie je iets wat we beter kunnen doen? Stuur dan een berichtje naar social@nos.nl

Je vindt de NOS de hele dag door op radio en televisie met het NOS Journaal, op NOS.nl en Facebook en Twitter. Altijd. Overal. NOS.

snippet.title: Nathan Zed
snippet.description:
I'm Nathan Zed

"DON'T FORGET TO SUBSCRIBE!!" I type, as I sit at my laptop, the rest of my body completely motionless.The click-clack sound of the keyboard echoing in my ears long after I had finished typing. I remain still for what seems like an eternity, only moving to wipe the single tear streaming from my right eye. "Not like this...", I let the whisper escape my lips loud enough for anyone nearby to hear me.
No one is nearby.

snippet.title: Dreamsea Surf Camps
snippet.description:
Welcome to Dreamsea Surf's official YouTube-Channel! This is the place where you'll get exclusive insights into our Surf destinations and the life of our Dreamsea family.

Dreamsea Surf is a place for friends, couples, solo travelers, and everyone who’s looking for active and social holidays. We believe in the human being, the slow travel concept, and that we can inspire others with kindness, friendliness, and happiness. All Dreamsea Surf Camps are carefully designed to create a cozy homey atmosphere to enlighten your senses and to make you feel part of the Dreamsea family. Dreamsea's core is the creation of a broad multicultural community where people can share their culture, values, and fun. Our goal is to create a sustainable, touristic environment by promoting respect for nature, a balanced lifestyle, and active healthy tourism through surf culture while providing unique experiences to people from all over the world.

AFP is a leading global news agency providing fast, comprehensive and verified coverage of the events shaping our world and the issues affecting our daily lives. Drawing from an unparalleled newsgathering network across 151 countries, AFP is also a world leader in digital verification. With 2,400 staff members from more than 100 different countries, AFP covers the world in six languages, with its unique brand of multimedia storytelling spanning video, text, photo and graphics.

If you want to know more about AFP’s offers or want to license a video, please follow this link 👉 http://u.afp.com/wvnD 
AFP’s services and content are for professional use only. 

AFP welcomes comments from our community on YouTube, but we do not tolerate any form of discrimination or hate speech. If these guidelines are violated, comments will be hidden or deleted by our community managers without prior agreement.

snippet.title: indusdotnews
snippet.description:
Aap Media Network believes in an informed and engaged citizenry, essential for a constitutional democracy. We provide relevant, important, timely and accurate news to the audience and opportunities for public discourse and interaction. In doing so, we are accountable to our viewers. We cherish our independence and strive to be objective and fair.

Our news-gathering and analyses seek to meet high editorial standards. We aim to inculcate civility in the discourse, an unfortunate casualty of the race for television rating points.

Our English-language channel, Indus News, aims to present Pakistan’s perspective on issues of regional and global importance through an inside-out view. We believe the viewer receives the greatest benefit from news and analyses in a global-to-local context. In this, we seek to bring to international audiences the complexity often missed in the coverage of this region

snippet.title: Hook Yarn Carabiner
snippet.description:
Hookyarncarabiner.com

Maker: Ellie | Crochet patterns and creative outlets for an outdoor life on the road. #hookyarncarabiner

Hello! I am Ellie and I am passionate about inspiring others to find their creative niche. I post free crochet patterns, tips, and techniques for exploration andI recently ended a year of #Vanlife with my husband. During our year of travel I discovered more about crochet than t last ten years combined. I am a self-taught crocheter and am always hungry to learn more. I decided to start a blog to share what I have learned and more fully join this creative community. When I am not crocheting, I am mountain biking, rock climbing, mountaineering, hiking, backpacking, paddling, and generally spending time outdoors in my local community. I want to bring an outdoorsy vibe to the crochet world and hope you love my patterns!

snippet.title: ChickenWire
snippet.description:
Interested in politics or going to Malaysia? Want to debate? It’s time to give YOU a voice. 
Every other day at 4pm. 

Each video is a forum for debate rather than a lecture. By opening up the conversation its providing a benefit to the country and the world as a whole and has the potential to make real change. 

ChickeWire stared off as a comedy channel and I still like to poke fun from time to time. The name ChickenWire actually comes from a song I made that went viral when I was younger https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qZ7HwBQ3C6o&t=7s

Ever since I've been making the odd political video when the UK election 2017 came round was when I gained a lot of views for this documentary I made https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ol9zSvJxj3M&t=10s

It was then I realised that even though I don't always predict things correctly I have a skill for seeing an oversight into how the UK works and I'm passionate about providing that information.

Explore the world. Subscribe.

snippet.title: Robotaki
snippet.description:
There is a lot more behind the name and the mask than most people may perceive. Coming in to the spotlight with his top-tier remix work (Just the Remixes.), and being recognized for his impeccable sounds, Preston Chin, the man behind the moniker has prepared himself to take on a much greater task. 

A task that entails enveloping the world with a powerful new take on funk, Electronic and disco. A responsibility to brighten peoples days and to make people dance. A quest to bring a fresh musical experience to humans that has never been done before. 

Armed with a Master's degree in Cell Biology, a carefully curated sound and support from the likes of Porter Robinson and Madeon,  he's the man to accomplish this mission.

snippet.title: Domonique Cynthia
snippet.description:
The power of the creative mind! There’s nothing else like it. I love problem solving through innovation. I found a passion for using my creativity, videography and storytelling skills to help showcase diversity across universities globally. My ultimate goal is to encourage people of color to see ourselves thriving in institutions that we have traditionally been underrepresented in. I aim to ensure that the doors opened for me are left opened even wider for those who will come next.

I am fascinated by a camera’s ability to capture the deepest intricacies of the human mind. Filmmaking is empowering. It allows me to create visually-captivating and emotionally-stirring stories. What’s most fascinating is a camera’s ability to be the tool that helps me continuously learn. With my eye in the viewfinder, there’s no longer a barrier between my creativity and the infinite inspiration the world offers. This is my passion.

snippet.title: NOS op 3
snippet.description:
NOS op 3 geeft uitleg bij het nieuws, in duidelijke taal. Doen we hier op YouTube, maar ook op Insta, TikTok en in de podcast Lang verhaal kort. 

Abonneer je op ons kanaal en praat mee in de comments. Heb je vragen, stel ze vooral in de comments. En als je een onderwerp hebt waar wij in jouw ogen écht een video over moeten maken, deel die dan! Vinden we leuk.

Hou je dan wel even hieraan:

snippet.title: The StudyTube Project
snippet.description:
Hello! 

The outbreak of the Coronavirus pandemic is having unprecedented impacts across the world: schools and universities are closing, GCSE and A-Level exams are cancelled - but that doesn’t mean education needs to stop.

So, we’ve decided to do something about it: welcome to The StudyTube Project!

We’ve all teamed up to try and bring calm in these times of high anxiety and stress. Each day for the foreseeable future, we’ll be taking it in turns to teach you something, or share an area of education we’re passionate about or specialize in. This is a channel to keep you busy, keep you learning or even just to give you somewhere to escape to! Any profits made from Adsense will go straight to charities helping fight COVID-19.

Let's come together as a community and support one another through this confusing time.

There will be a brand new video every day at 6pm, as well as regular content on our Instagram: @thestudytubeproject !

snippet.title: El Machetero
snippet.description:
Gracias por brindar tu amistad


Hola Amigo. como comprenderás el hecho de ser piloto de las FAR no me permite darme el lujo de permitir que las personas de buena fe que quieran conocerme carguen con las responsabilidad de tener algún dato mío. Si, vivo en Cuba y soy militar. en estos momentos están removiendo cielo y tierra alrededor mio para encontrarme pero de momento estoy haciendo las cosas bien y no me van a encontrar. Represento a cientos de soldados y oficiales que están en desacuerdo con la dictadura cubana. Somos del ejercito, la marina y la aviación en mi caso. Estamos recuperando datos de todos los delitos militares que se están cometiendo bajo el amparo de la dictadura para en su momento juzgarlos con toda la fuerza de la constitución cubana y la democracia que esperemos que se instaure al final de nuestra lucha.Las cosas que publico en mi blog tresdobleV punto elojosobrecuba puntocom son enviadas a traves de amigos que viajan a Europa con frecuencia y yo envío los DVDs con videos e información escrita para que los suban en mi blog. No tengo internet aunque se como tenerl por las malas de vez en cuando como es el caso de hoy. Por la particularidad de mi estado no puedo contar con apoyo de los que están de mi lado aunque estemos por la misma causa, entonces esto que llevo es una guerra solitaria y tiene que ser así por la seguridad mia y de mis compañeros. Por eso rechazo todas las peticiones de amistad en youtube y blogger para que nadie sepa mas datos que los que yo dejo saber a proposito, te pido mil disculpas por no aceptar el contacto y espero que entiendas que es por el bien de nuestro objetivo comun.De momento te doy las gracias por visitar mis videos y mi blog y espero que extiendas desde tus posibilidades toda la información que a duras penas logro subir a este espacio.
Un saludo afectuoso.
Elmachetero

snippet.title: Gabriel Jose Rodriguez
snippet.description:
Musician, producer, DJ, and Funk music enthusiast alike, Gabriel hails out of Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. Gabriel drew much of his musical influence from his father, a well-known Latin composer and lead musician for his band La Unica.

Interested in music all his life, Gabriel pursued it further at Eastern University where he completed a degree in Music Composition and Electronic Music.

When he’s not performing, he spends time in his studio creating his own music and completing client projects. Although he is well versed in all genres of music, some of Gabriel’s favorite genres to mix include Funk/Motown, Oldies, Hip Hop, R&B, Top 40, and Pop music.

Aided by a decade of piano lessons and a musically influenced upbringing, Gabriel’s diverse background lends to his effortless ability to blend a variety of genres; creating the perfect backdrop for any event!

snippet.title: London Mural Artist Alessandra Tortone
snippet.description:
I am Alessandra Tortone, leading London mural artist with over 20 years experience providing bespoke mural art services to an extensive list of clients. 

My specialty is internal and external mural art including: wall murals, hand painted window murasls, graffiti street murals, shutter & hoarding murals and menus & chalkboards. All projects are bespoke and unique to the clients’ specification.

I work with corporate clients, charities, councils, high street shops, residential clients, school’s, hospitals, pubs and restaurants, and Business Improvement Districts (BID). I have the creativity and experience to take your project to the next level.

My projects take me all over the world. If you would like one of my murals, please contact me via my website, including details of your project and its location.

snippet.title: TRT World Now
snippet.description:
At TRT World we're building a global community focused around change. We’re looking beyond the headlines to drive meaningful conversations that empower. We want to connect people across the globe to issues that matter. We explore the reality behind the hashtags and the people behind the statistics. We will seek to unpack the issues behind each story.

By placing the human at the heart of each story we hope to promote a global conscience that provokes moral reactions - revealing a deeper understanding of the diversity of the lives around us.

Subscribe to our channel for all our latest in-depth, on the ground reporting from around the world.

Nuestro canal de YouTube tiene todo esto y más, ofreciendo contenidos seleccionados y originales de la principal fuente de noticias internacionales de Europa.

Nuestra misión es capacitar a la gente para que se forme su propia opinión. Confiamos en la inteligencia y la capacidad de las personas para decidir por sí mismas y tratamos de ofrecer a nuestra audiencia la mayor diversidad de puntos de vista a través de un periodismo inexcusablemente imparcial.

Euronews nació de la voluntad de crear un fuerte canal de noticias europeo independiente. Como único medio de comunicación internacional con una perspectiva europea, Euronews es el lugar al que el mundo acude para escuchar lo que Europa tiene que decir.

snippet.title: A&M TECHNOLOGY
snippet.description: The word "technology" can also be used to refer to a collection of techniques. In this context, it is the current state of humanity's knowledge of how to combine resources to produce desired products, to solve problems, fulfill needs, or satisfy wants; it includes technical methods, skills, processes, techniques, tools and raw materials. When combined with another term, such as "medical technology" or "space technology," it refers to the state of the respective field's knowledge and tools. "State-of-the-art technology" refers to the high technology available to humanity in any field.

snippet.title: euronews (in Italiano)
snippet.description:
Benvenuti al canale Youtube ufficiale di Euronews! 

Tutti i giorni, a tutte le ore, la nostra squadra di 500 giornalisti provenienti da oltre 30 Paesi lavora per raccontarvi l'Europa con assoluta imparzialità. Su questo canale trovate una selezione dei migliori contenuti della TV europea per eccellenza. 

La nostra missione è quella di dare alle persone la possibilità di formarsi una propria opinione. Confidiamo nell'intelligenza e nella capacità delle persone di decidere da sole e cerchiamo di fornire al nostro pubblico la più grande diversità di punti di vista attraverso un giornalismo imparziale.
Ci concentriamo su fatti, idee e soluzioni.
Crediamo che tutti i punti di vista siano importanti.

Euronews è nato dalla volontà di creare un canale d'informazione europeo indipendente. Essendo l'unico media internazionale con una prospettiva europea, Euronews è il luogo a cui si rivolge il mondo per ascoltare ciò che l'Europa ha da dire.

snippet.title: Tait Martinez
snippet.description:
Tait Martinez 's Bio

Tait Martinez.... is a singer/rapper /producer from Birmingham. He makes his own music, co-produce beats, write his own songs and for other artists, and also plays musical instruments such as piano, guitar and saxophone. Tait Martinez is into all kinds of music but mainly jazz, soul music, classical, rnb , electro house, pop and hip-hop. His music style and sound is different from the usual urban artists. Tait Martinez dwells on creating own sound, own style and he is very versatile with a music style which is a merge involving urban / rnb/ jazz, pop music, dance and electro house put together. 
Tait Martinez's interest in music started at a very early young age singing in school choir, church choir, at weddings and other ceremonies/events. Lately he's been recording his material and now has over 20 tracks for his debut album due soon.. The Album is entitled Life Is A Journey. You can follow Lyfe Martinez on twitter - @LyfeMartinez

snippet.title: Jordan Ware
snippet.description: Jordan Waré is grammy- award winning producer, violinist, and one half of the indie group, October's Child. The trained violinist has performed worldwide with such acts as Madonna, Quincy Jones, Justin TImberlake and Wyclef Jean. A native New Yorker who moved to Los Angeles in mid-2014, Waré has continued to further develop his production sound, producing for numerous up and coming artists including, Avonlea, Elley Duhé & Brent Faiyaz . Waré touts his greatest accolade as co-producing the ballad that would become the hit record, "Where Are Ü Now," featuring Justin Bieber on Diplo and Skrillex's Jack Ü album, which won a Grammy's in 2016 for Best Dance Recording and Best Dance/Electronic Album.

snippet.title: Your Local Harry
snippet.description:
I'm Your Local Harry. There are others like me.... but, I am yours. - Basically, I'm just a goofball from the Eugene area. You might know me for playing music & you might know me for making videos where I film weddings, commercials, etc. -- I do both. I posted descriptions below but if you'd like to see examples of what I do, please visit my web site at www.YourLocalHarry.com
-----
Music -- You might have seen me jamming out around town. I play several instruments & I combine everything live using a loop pedal. I don't use backing tracks & I don't use laptops or pre-recorded samples. I play covers & originals & I am currently accepting gigs in the Eugene area.
-----
Videos - You may have seen one of my video projects. I've been fortunate to serve as director and producer for several wedding videos, commercials, & instructional videos. I'm always interested in hearing about new projects, so if you have a special event you'd like filmed, contact me on my web site www.YourLocalHarry.com

snippet.title: [artisthony]
snippet.description:
Hello, my name is Anthony Jones, a Haitian American Animator. I began my creative journey at a young age, thanks to the encouragement of my parents, my mother being American, and my father being Haitian. My creative work tends to have some bearing to the aesthetics I saw as a child in the late 2000s, and multiculturism, especially the Afro-Latin American experience. I believe in a world that promotes learning about the many groups of people that make it, and that dream can be promoted and achieved through the power of animation.

🇺🇸/🇭🇹 (20 Y/O)

snippet.title: Hudson County View
snippet.description:
Hudson County View is an independent media outlet covering news and politics for Hudson County, NJ, and all of its municipalities. Owned and operated by John Heinis, an investigative reporter, Hudson County View focuses on covering elections, public policy, lawsuits, corruption and all other things related to government and politics in Hudson County.

Our slogan, "The Eye of the Community," is to signify our commitment to making sure the voices of the people are heard. In America, one of the main functions of the press is to keep government open and honest, and that's what we aim to do here in Hudson County.

snippet.description:

From barefoot lifestyle (yes, it's legal and safe) to witch craft and spells - Randym will walk you through their experiences .

Barefoot Living
EVP and Paranormal Experiences
Randym being Random
Magnet Fishing Adventures
Witchy Wednesdays 
Geode Hunting and Rock Hounding

These will expand to include Crafting and Painting, and more as the seasons change. 

Oh, I'm also the Friendly Felon and if you have a background (like I do) - feel free to check out thefriendlyfelon.com for tips that I used to pull myself out of the gutters after my conviction. You'll find information on bonding, background checks, housing, and so much more! I even literally wrote the book on it!

snippet.title: AVCA Volleyball
snippet.description: The American Volleyball Coaches Association, which was founded Oct. 26, 1981, seeks to advance the sport of volleyball with coaches at the epicenter of leadership, advocacy, and professional development. The association membership includes more than 9,500 collegiate, professional, high school, club, and youth volleyball coaches—primarily in the United States. The AVCA represents women’s volleyball, men’s volleyball, and beach volleyball coaches, and works to increase exposure and recognition for the sport of volleyball.
